data.description: Charming and Affordable ranch near downtown Newnan. So much privacy on a 1.49 acre lot not in a neighborhood! Spacious rooms, high ceilings,  kitchen with beautiful granite and tile back splash, stainless appliances including refrigerator, baths with granite and upgraded rectangular sinks, upgraded large tile, master bath has double vanities with granite tops, spacious master walk-in closet, new roof, new siding, new hot water heater, new dishwasher, faux wood nice blinds throughout, oversized 8 x 20 (approx.) patio off kitchen in large (nice wood)  fenced private backyard, lots of natural light.  So much for the price!
